6. Waits for the worker thread to complete
7. Records thread safety status after the guard
8. Records thread count after the guard
9. Returns all the collected state information

The `ThreadRegistrationGuard` is used both in the main thread scope and inside the worker thread to properly test its functionality. The worker thread includes a small delay to ensure it stays alive long enough for proper testing.

